festival/"&gt;Coheed 和 Cambria 正在举办自己的音乐节&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.vice.com"&gt;VICE&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 19:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.vice.com/en/article/coheed-and-cambria-are-launching-their-own-festival/</guid></item></channel></rss>